                           <locus target="#00" n="#"> Fol. 76ra-b: Donation note.</locus>
                           <q xml:lang="gez"> Fol. 76ra-b: ዝንቱ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ዘተሣየጠቶ፡ በንዋያ፡ ቅድስት፡ ወህሪት፡ ወለተ፡ መድኅን፡ ወወ[ሀ]በቶ፡ ለቅዱስ፡ ሚካኤል፡ ደንዴራ፡ ከመ፡ ይኩኖ፡ መድኃኒተ፡ ነፍስ፡ ወሥጋ፡ ለአቡሃ፡ ወለእማ፡ ገብረ፡ ዮሐ[ን]ስ፡ ወለተ፡ ገብርኤል፡ ወለደቂቃ፡ ወለተ፡ አቢየ፡ እግዚእ፡ ወለተ፡ ተክለ፡ ሃይማኖት፡ ዘሰረቃ፡ ወዘፋሐቃ፡ ወዘተአገላ፡ በስልጣነ፡ ጴጥሮስ፡ ወጳውሎስ፡ ውጉዘ፡ ለይኩን፡</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- The title መደሃን የአለም is written on the front cover with white paint.&#xD;
- Tämälläs-sign, in the shape of a cross (+) indicating the place where the omissions, written in the left margin, belong: fol. 11va.&#xD;
- Omitted letters or words inserted interlineally in the main hand: e.g., fols. 4vb, 6va, 22va, 43ra, 48ra, 55vb.&#xD;
- Omitted letter inserted in blue pen in a secondary hand: fol. 5rb.&#xD;
- Erasures: fols. 20ra, 26vb, 33rb.&#xD;
- Erasure marked with thin red lines: fol. 44rb.&#xD;
- Immediate corrections indicated by thin black lines or series of dashes above and below the word(s): e.g., fols. 4vb, 5va, 10ra, 22rb, 32vb, 46vb, 50rb, 58vb.&#xD;
- Space for rubrication left unfilled: fol. 48va.&#xD;
- Unfilled line marked with thin red lines: fol. 17rb.&#xD;
- Notes in pencil on fols. 2r, 76v.&#xD;
- Several names are written in the supplication formulas in a secondary hand (possibly the same as Additio 1) in brilliant vermillion ink: Gäbrä ʾIyäsus (e.g., fols. 7rb, 11rb, 25rb, 36va, 57va), Wälättä Mädḫǝn (e.g., fols. 11rb, 19ra, 30vb, 46vb, 57va, 70va), ʾabunä Kidanä Maryam (e.g., fols. 10vb, 22ra, 32ra, 50rb, 62vb, 70va), Wälättä ʾAbiyä ʾƎgziʾ (e.g., fols. 10vb, 22ra, 28vb, 53va, 62vb, 70va), Gäbrä Yoḥannǝs (fol. 70va), Wälättä Gäbrǝʾel (fol. 70va). The name of Täsfa Ḥǝywät is crudely written in red pencil in the supplication formulas e.g., on fols. 7rb, 11rb, 15ra, 44va, 56va, 66ra, 76ra.</item>
                     </list>
